                                    <p>Hello <strong style="color: #739cd2;">{!relatedTo.Contact__r.FirstName}</strong>,</p>
                                    <p>Congratulations!</p>
                                    <p>You are now producing clean renewable energy from the sun.  Again, thank you for partnering with SunPower. </p>
                                    <table style="font-family: Arial, sans-sarif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.25em; color: #695e49; border-collapse: collapse;">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="border: 1px solid #fdb823; background: #fdb823; padding: .5em 1em .5em 1em; margin-top: 0;"><strong>A List of Helpful Resources</strong></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="border: 1px solid #fdb823; padding-right: 1em; padding-top: 16px;">
                                                <ul style="margin-top: 0;">
                                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;"><strong>SunPower Welcome Kit</strong><br/>
                                                        Your SunPower Welcome Kit is in the mail! Included in this kit is a SunPower User Manual to help answer any questions on 
                                                        your leased system. We've also attached an electronic version of the SunPower User Manual to this message. 
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;"><strong>Your First Billing Statement </strong><br/>
                                                        Your first statement is being processed. You can expect to receive it in 30-60 days.<br/><br/>
                                                        <strong>Note:</strong> You will still receive a bill from your utility company. As each utility company is different, 
                                                            be sure to contact them to make sure you√≠re on the right rate plan for solar. Most companies will utilize plans such 
                                                            as "time of use", so inquire to get the best rate possible. <strong style="color: #739cd2;">{!relatedTo.Opportunity__r.Owner.Name}</strong> can assist you with this, 
                                                            feel free to call and discuss.
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;"><strong>Monitor Your Energy Production Online </strong><br/>
                                                        By now, your installation team has helped get you logged into your online monitoring system.  
                                                        This gives you the ability to <a href="https://monitor.us.sunpower.com/" style="color: #739cd2;">see how much energy your system is producing.</a> 
                                                        You can also download the SunPower Monitoring app for your <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/genre/ios/id36?mt=8" style="color: #739cd2;">iPhone</a><sup style="margin-top: -4px; display: inline-block; font-size: 11px;">&reg;</sup>, 
                                                        <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/genre/ios/id36?mt=8" style="color: #739cd2;">iPad</a><sup style="margin-top: -4px; display: inline-block; font-size: 11px;">&reg;</sup>, or <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sunpowercorp.sp001&hl=en" style="color: #739cd2;">Android</a><sup style="margin-top: -4px; display: inline-block; font-size: 11px;">&trade;</sup> mobile device  
                                                        Yet another great way to share with friends and family how much clean renewable energy you are producing!
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;"><strong>Installation Experience Survey</strong><br/>
                                                        You'll soon receive an email invitation to take a survey. It's important to us that you've had a fantastic experience; 
                                                        please let us know if we have delivered it. Remember you can contact us anytime at <strong style="color: #739cd2;">1-800-SUNPOWER</strong>.
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;"><strong>Annual Energy Production Report </strong><br/>
                                                        SunPower monitors your system performance.  Following your 1-year anniversary, and for every year thereafter, 
                                                        you will receive our Annual Energy Production Guarantee report that summarizes your system's energy production for the year.
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li style="margin-bottom: 16px;"><strong>Write a Review </strong><br/>
                                                        Share your experience with <strong style="color: #739cd2;">{!relatedTo.Opportunity__r.Installer__r.Name}</strong> and <a href="http://us.sunpower.com/dealers-installers/find-dealer-installer/" style="color: #739cd2;">write a review</a>
                                                        and help other customers learn about the great installer you worked with.<br/>
                                                        <em>*See web page for terms and conditions relating to submission of review.</em>
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li><strong>Refer a Friend </strong><br/>
                                                        Going solar is a message you can feel good about passing along. 
                                                        To help spread the word while earning referral rewards, login to the <a href="http://www.sharesunpower.com/m/133343599" style="color: #739cd2;">SunPower Referral Center</a>.
                                                    </li>
